title: Grateful Dead Live at Alpine Valley Music Theatre on 1984-07-07
lineage: Master Cassette > Nak CR7a > Korg MR1000 5.6 mhz 1 bit > Audiogate render > Flac 16/44
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Dire Wolf, Minglewood Blues, Dupree's Diamond Blues, My Brother Esau, Brown Eyed Women, Looks Like Rain-> Might As Well

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Cold Rain & Snow-> Playin' In The Band-> China Doll-> Drums-> Terrapin Station-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away-> Turn On Your Love Light-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace
